## Key Takeaway

This project demonstrates how AI-driven incentive optimization can reduce reward spending by **14%+** while maintaining a structured, data-driven approach to retention management.

The broader objective is to help rewarded user acquisition platforms maximize profitability without blindly reducing incentives.

